article.headline: Adkins' 17 lead South Carolina Upstate over Brevard 91-60
article.description: — Carmelo Adkins' 17 points helped South Carolina Upstate defeat Brevard 91-60 on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Adkins' 17 lead South Carolina Upstate over Brevard 91-60
article.story: SPARTANBURG, S.C. -- — Carmelo Adkins' 17 points helped South Carolina Upstate defeat Brevard 91-60 on Wednesday night. Adkins also contributed seven rebounds for the Spartans (3-8). Mister Dean scored 16 points and added six rebounds and three steals. Chico Johnson shot 4 of 9 from the field, including 1 for 3 from 3-point range, and went 2 for 4 from the line to finish with 11 points. Jadon Carnes led the way for the Tornados with 11 points. Charlie Hester added eight points and Andrew Smith had seven points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
